The paper deals with the problem of image-text matching, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, the paper also uses attention mechanisms and deep learning techniques, which are common in sub-fields such as natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and multimedia (cs.MM).
